<p><cite>The Furies</cite>, by Katie Lowe. <cite>The Craft</cite> meets <cite>The Secret History</cite> with a dash of <cite>The Stranger Diaries</cite> and <cite>Girl in Snow</cite>, with believable teenage characters in a grotty seaside town - 4*</p>

