<p><cite>Big Sky</cite>, by Kate Atkinson. Such a treat to be reunited with Jackson Brodie! Something I especially love about Atkinsonâ€™s books is that pretty much all the characters are fully fleshed-out, with insights into their thoughts and humorous observations of, and from, them. Even the dogs have distinct personalities - 5*</p>

